reviewText: As someone who already owned Butterflies and Justine and Juliet, I decided to give this a look. First, this movie contains hard core explicit sex although no "Money" shots. It actually turned out to be a fun & funny movie. It is about an over sexed Eva whose Sister & Guardian decides to put her in a private school to teach some morality. I think maybe she should have researched this school a little better as it was the perfect place for an over heated Eva. Eventually, a Lawyer from the Board of Education shows up on a fact finding mission. Well he eventually gets his facts. The real fun begins when Eva's sister shows up and she and the lawyer decide to do an investigation. That alone was worth the price of the movie in my opinion. I am still chuckling as I write this. The overall quality of the movie was good. I think you will find yourself laughing as I did.I am not much for comedy as a general rule, but I thoroughly enjoyed this. Charlie S.
summary: Lots of Explicit Sex, But Enjoyable
